<p><strong>拉氏变换法</strong><br /><span class="katex-error" title="ParseError: KaTeX parse error: {align} can be used only in display mode." style="color:#cc0000">\begin{align}
&amp; \begin{cases}
u_{i}(t) =Ri(t)+L \frac{d}{dt}i(t)+\frac{1}{C}\int i(t) \, dt \\
u_{o}(t)=\frac{1}{C}\int i(t) \, dt \to i(t) = C \frac{du_{o}(t)}{dt}
